Also remove this completely
#rebuilt-popup-style {
    height: calc(90vh - 150px) !important;
    overflow: auto;
}

because your popup uses:

class="rebuilt-popup-style"

not

id="rebuilt-popup-style"

and having both floating around often causes confusion later.

